    <item>
      <title>Desjardins 表示，加拿大无力阻止临时居民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/canada-can-t-afford-to-block-temporary-residents-desjardins-economist-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加鼎证券表示，限制进入加拿大的临时工和国际学生数量将加深预期的经济衰退，并削弱该国随后的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/canada-can-t-afford-to-block-temporary-residents-desjardins-economist-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 14:16:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
